varao sa svojom sekretaricom.

178
00:16:52,135 --> 00:16:54,768
Koristili su sve
hotele u blizini.

179
00:16:54,935 --> 00:16:56,868
I to ne jeftine.

180
00:16:56,935 --> 00:16:59,769
Drolja je volela da širi noge

181
00:16:59,869 --> 00:17:01,769
ali samo na satenu.

182
00:17:02,269 --> 00:17:04,269
Zato je uzimao
novac iz kase.

183
00:17:04,402 --> 00:17:07,436
U početku malo,
a onda 50 miliona.

184
00:17:08,403 --> 00:17:10,836
Odleteli su za Panamu.

185
00:17:12,737 --> 00:17:14,237
Popij!

186
00:17:15,970 --> 00:17:18,504
