207
00:18:39,245 --> 00:18:41,412
Zovem se Madeleine Wells.

208
00:18:41,579 --> 00:18:44,579
Madeleine, kao
Marija Magdalena.

209
00:18:44,913 --> 00:18:46,913
Plakala je?

210
00:18:47,079 --> 00:18:52,180
Wells, kao u vodi.
