464
00:42:45,923 --> 00:42:47,390
Zaboravi.

465
00:42:47,990 --> 00:42:49,457
Da? - Mauresque.

466
00:42:49,624 --> 00:42:51,457
Maraska za mladića.

467
00:42:51,757 --> 00:42:55,458
Jedna maraska
i dva gazirana soka.

468
00:42:55,624 --> 00:42:58,691
Je li predbračni ili
posle muvanja?

469
00:42:58,858 --> 00:43:00,791
Jesi li uroðeni kreten?

470
00:43:02,558 --> 00:43:04,992
