Primećujem šta?

512
00:45:50,142 --> 00:45:52,475
Uvek sedi ovde, jel' tako?

513
00:45:53,209 --> 00:45:54,642
Sedi.

514
00:45:55,642 --> 00:45:57,309
Sedi Georgette.

515
00:45:58,876 --> 00:46:00,609
Šta vidiš?

516
00:46:00,843 --> 00:46:03,310
Moj štand za cigarete.

517
00:46:03,510 --> 00:46:05,177
Ništa ne nedostaje?

518
00:46:05,643 --> 00:46:07,277
Ništa.

519
00:46:07,777 --> 00:46:09,310
Potrudi se.

520
00:46:16,311 --> 00:46:18,711
Ne vidim šta!

521
00:46:19,111 --> 00:46:21,745
Razmisli o tome.
Laku noć.

522
00:46:39,213 --> 00:46:40,647
Dobar dan.

523
00:46:41,714 --> 00:46:45,347
Pismo kasni 30 godina.

524
00:46:45,514 --> 00:46:49,981
Torbu sa pismima koju su našli
planinari na glečeru Mont Blana

525
00:46:50,114 --> 00:46:51,781
je bila deo tovara

526
00:46:51,848 --> 00:46:55,648
izgubljenog u padu
aviona krajem 60-tih.

527
00:46:56,682 --> 00:47:00,149
Baš tužno!
Lepa mlada princeza.

528
00:47:00,415 --> 00:47:02,582
A ne smeta ako je
stara i  ružna?

529
00:47:02,716 --> 00:47:05,049
Svakako!
Pogledaj Majku Terezu.

530
00:47:06,716 --> 00:47:09,583
Još uvek juri za Ginom?

531
00:47:10,250 --> 00:47:12,283
Ne, ima drugu.

532
00:47:12,883 --> 00:47:14,950
Neko koga znam?

533
00:47:15,284 --> 00:47:18,050
